---
/**
 * BioSection.astro
 * Bloque de bio textual en About.
 * Headline editorial + dos párrafos de descripción.
 */
---

<section class="space-y-6" aria-labelledby="bio-heading">

  <!-- Sup-label de sección -->
  <p class="section-label text-secondary">About the Architect</p>

  <!-- Headline editorial con clamp tipográfico -->
  <h1
    id="bio-heading"
    class="font-headline font-bold text-on-surface leading-tight tracking-tighter"
    style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);"
  >
    Bridging the gap between{" "}
    <span class="text-primary">Logic</span>{" "}
    and{" "}
    <span class="text-tertiary">Scale</span>.
  </h1>

  <!-- Cuerpo de texto -->
  <div class="space-y-4 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg font-body">
    <p>
      I am Carlos, a systems architect and automation specialist dedicated to
      building resilient digital infrastructures. With over a decade of
      experience, I&apos;ve navigated the transition from manual precision to
      autonomous systems.
    </p>
    <p>
      My philosophy is rooted in <em class="text-on-surface not-italic font-medium">technical elegance</em>:
      the belief that the most complex infrastructure should operate with the
      rhythm of a heartbeat&mdash;consistent, quiet, and essential. Whether
      I&apos;m deploying multi-cloud environments or training AI agents for QA,
      my focus remains on high-velocity reliability.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
